{"tid":2160874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白羅斯反對派領袖稱準備領導國家　促保安部隊「變節」","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T13:15:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c152ec2741c74feb846ab838e6938ac7323a3d74","tid":2160874,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544152-20200817.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544152-20200817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=4ea90aee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544152-20200817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=51f7ed5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544152-20200817.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n大批示威者在白羅斯首都明斯克抗議，不滿總統選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n示威者要求總統盧卡申科辭職，又促請當局釋放政治犯。<br />\n<br />\n參選總統落敗的反對派候選人季哈諾夫斯卡婭表示，準備領導國家，呼籲建立法律機制，以確保再次舉行公正的總統選舉。<br />\n<br />\n身在立陶宛季哈諾夫斯卡婭發表錄影講話，敦促安全和執法人員「變節」，揚言會原諒他們過去所犯的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n而盧卡申科在親政府集會上形容反對派是鼠輩，又關注北約即將在波蘭及立陶宛的軍事演習，大肆抨擊西方的軍事聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n另外，盧卡申科連續第二日同俄羅斯總統普京通電話，普京重申確保白羅斯安全。"},{"pid":"8b47c9ff2a7432f26f81b0deaec2750b1433ce1e","tid":2160874,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"呢幾年個世界好似拍戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5abc0a3f38a81f0417a9e25b5a2e12caf1320e","tid":2160874,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"希望白羅斯義士, 有足夠武器頂住俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n唔夠, 就拿拿臨去鄰國烏克蘭買住黑市先, 頂住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 